{"type":"message","id":"3b898499","parentId":"5126960d","timestamp":"2026-04-22T04:20:30.002Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-22 12:20:27 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b51b0866758acc4e42a35d0e1fec]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b0866758acc4e42a35d0e1fec\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 12:20 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\nhttps://my.feishu.cn/docx/GTh8di7JvopqcBxIALKcryconUc?from=from_copylink"}],"timestamp":1776831630000}}
