{"type":"message","id":"2e5a5075","parentId":"595cd522","timestamp":"2026-04-22T04:36:38.545Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to add the main content. Let me write a comprehensive script that adds all the major sections. I'll use the Lark-flavored markdown approach with update-doc, but since that might not work, let me try to use the block API directly with the key sections.\n\nLet me write a Python script to generate all the blocks needed for the v4.0 document content.\n\nThe v4.0 content structure:\n1. Title block (already created)\n2. Version info quote (already created)\n3. Divider (already created)\n4. Table of Contents\n5. Section 1: 精准流量词 → TK精准标签词\n6. Section 2: 评估新品短视频种草友好度\n\n\n7. Section 3: 投产比与资金效率\n8. Section 4: 差异化 + 供应链匹配度\n9. Section 5: 进场时间节点（旺季前置）\n10. Section 6: 季节性 / 节日性 / 活动产品\n11. Section 7: 合规与侵权风险（保命项）\n12. Section 8: 发货数量 + 变体循环布局\n13. 综合评分系统（满分170分）\n14. 三轨道选品策略\n15. 飞书多维表格配置\n\nGiven the complexity of constructing all these blocks individually, I'm thinking it might be more efficient to use the update API with markdown content instead. But the create-doc tool didn't work earlier due to permission issues, so I should test whether feishu_mcp_create_doc has the same limitation. For now, I'll continue with the block API and build out the content section by section through a Python script."},{"type":"text","text":"Now let me write the full v4.0 content via block API. I'll do it in batches:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5647fe12deec41abb61ffe48","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"DOC_ID=\"Y4ysdhBDjouNO0xmejBcGaXGn7b\"\nTOKEN=\"t-g1044mcoRMJVN7IVRN43TBBLD6TJU5YD73QHYG3X\"\n\n# Helper to add blocks\nadd_blocks() {\n  curl -s -X POST \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/${DOC_ID}/blocks/${DOC_ID}/children\" \\\n    -H \"Authorization: Bearer ${TOKEN}\" \\\n    -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n    -d \"$(printf '%s' \"$1\")\"\n}\n\n# Section: 目录\nadd_blocks '{\n  \"children\": [\n    {\"block_type\": 4, \"heading2\": {\"elements\": [{\"text_run\": {\"content\": \"📋 目录\", \"text_element_style\": {}}}], \"style\": {\"align\": 1, \"folded\": false}}},\n    {\"block_type\": 13, \"ordered\": {\"elements\": [{\"text_run\": {\"content\": \"精准流量词 → TK精准标签词（一切分析的基础）\", \"text_element_style\": {}}}], \"style\": {\"align\": 1, \"folded\": false}}},\n    {\"block_type\": 13, \"ordered\": {\"elements\": [{\"text_run\": {\"content\": \"评估新品短视频种草友好度（新品好不好起）\", \"text_element_style\": {}}}], \"style\": {\"align\": 1, \"folded\": false}}},\n    {\"block_type\": 13, \"ordered\": {\"elements\": [{\"text_run\": {\"content\": \"投产比与资金效率\", \"text_element_style\": {}}}], \"style\": {\"align\": 1, \"folded\": false}}},\n    {\"block_type\": 13, \"ordered\": {\"elements\": [{\"text_run\": {\"content\": \"差异化 + 供应链匹配度\", \"text_element_style\": {}}}], \"style\": {\"align\": 1, \"folded\": false}}},\n    {\"block_type\": 13, \"ordered\": {\"elements\": [{\"text_run\": {\"content\": \"进场时间节点（旺季前置）\", \"text_element_style\": {}}}], \"style\": {\"align\": 1, \"folded\": false}}},\n    {\"block_type\": 13, \"ordered\": {\"elements\": [{\"text_run\": {\"content\": \"季节性 / 节日性 / 活动产品\", \"text_element_style\": {}}}], \"style\": {\"align\": 1, \"folded\": false}}},\n    {\"block_type\": 13, \"ordered\": {\"elements\": [{\"text_run\": {\"content\": \"合规与侵权风险（保命项）\", \"text_element_style\": {}}}], \"style\": {\"align\": 1, \"folded\": false}}},\n    {\"block_type\": 13, \"ordered\": {\"elements\": [{\"text_run\": {\"content\": \"发货数量 + 变体循环布局\", \"text_element_style\": {}}}], \"style\": {\"align\": 1, \"folded\": false}}},\n    {\"block_type\": 13, \"ordered\": {\"elements\": [{\"text_run\": {\"content\": \"综合评分系统（满分170分）\", \"text_element_style\": {}}}], \"style\": {\"align\": 1, \"folded\": false}}},\n    {\"block_type\": 13, \"ordered\": {\"elements\": [{\"text_run\": {\"content\": \"三轨道选品策略\", \"text_element_style\": {}}}], \"style\": {\"align\": 1, \"folded\": false}}},\n    {\"block_type\": 13, \"ordered\": {\"elements\": [{\"text_run\": {\"content\": \"飞书多维表格配置\", \"text_element_style\": {}}}], \"style\": {\"align\": 1, \"folded\": false}}},\n    {\"block_type\": 13, \"ordered\": {\"elements\": [{\"text_run\": {\"content\": \"工作节奏与行为准则\", \"text_element_style\": {}}}], \"style\": {\"align\": 1, \"folded\": false}}}\n  ],\n  \"index\": -1\n}'","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776832586764,"responseId":"0637834b438418c62337173ad49e0957"}}
