{"type":"message","id":"bc77d0ae","parentId":"465efc7b","timestamp":"2026-04-22T04:36:56.874Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Table cells can't be created directly as top-level blocks. I need to use the proper lark-table format or create the table as a whole. Let me use the lark-table format with proper structure, or I can just use text blocks to create the table rows. \n\nActually, looking at the SKILL.md, I see that for creating tables via API, I should use the `<lark-table>` format. But since I'm using the raw block API, I need to create a table block with children cells.\n\nLet me try a different approach - create a table block with proper structure. Actually looking at the block types, table_cell (type 32) needs to be children of a table block (type 31).\n\n\nI need to step back and use the document creation API instead of trying to work around the block API limitations. For a document this large, the feishu-create-doc tool with Lark-flavored Markdown would be much more efficient, but I'm running into permission issues with user tokens. Let me try a simpler approach using text blocks with formatted content instead."},{"type":"text","text":"Table API 需要特殊结构，用 Markdown 格式通过 update-doc 追加会更高效。让我换方式——用 create-doc 的 markdown 方式创建完整内容，然后不断追加：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_49421dd7112f4dddb8dba751","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"DOC_ID=\"Y4ysdhBDjouNO0xmejBcGaXGn7b\"\nTOKEN=\"t-g1044mcoRMJVN7IVRN43TBBLD6TJU5YD73QHYG3X\"\n\n# Try using raw_content API to write markdown\ncurl -s -X PATCH \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/docx/v1/documents/${DOC_ID}/raw_content\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer ${TOKEN}\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"content\": \"# v4.0 Test\\n\\nParagraph 1\"}'","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776832610614,"responseId":"0637836278417817c5d211291602e16d"}}
